sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Sidecar
    participant VLLM as vLLM API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Runner as HPUModelRunner<br/>(vllm_gaudi)
    participant HPU as Gaudi HPU<br/>SynapseAI Driver
    participant Peer as Peer HPUWorkers<br/>HCCL

    Note over Client,Peer: Flow 1: LLM Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (JWT)
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward (TLS terminated)
    KRBAC->>KRBAC: Validate JWT<br/>Check RBAC policy
    KRBAC->>VLLM: HTTP/8000 (localhost)<br/>No auth (trusted)
    VLLM->>Runner: Python in-process call<br/>Tokenize + Schedule
    Runner->>HPU: Execute via habana_frameworks.torch<br/>PCIe / SynapseAI

    opt Multi-Card Tensor Parallelism
        HPU->>Peer: HCCL Collective Ops<br/>RDMA/TCP (plaintext)
        Peer-->>HPU: Aggregated Results
    end

    HPU-->>Runner: Generated Tokens
    Runner-->>VLLM: Decoded Response
    VLLM-->>KRBAC: JSON Response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Forward Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,Peer: Flow 2: KV Cache Transfer (Disaggregated Serving)

    participant PrefillW as Prefill HPUWorker
    participant NIXLConn as NIXL Connector<br/>UCX Transport
    participant DecodeW as Decode HPUWorker<br/>(Remote)

    PrefillW->>NIXLConn: Python in-process call<br/>Transfer KV cache
    NIXLConn->>DecodeW: UCX (RDMA/GDR)<br/>plaintext, dynamic port
    DecodeW->>DecodeW: DMA to Local<br/>HPU KV Cache Memory

    Note over Client,Peer: Model Loading (Startup)

    participant S3 as S3/HuggingFace<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    VLLM->>S3: Download Model Weights<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / AWS IAM
    S3-->>VLLM: Model Artifacts
    VLLM->>HPU: Load Weights to HPU Memory
